Nyenǣsyanda ŋodq maqniwq ŋarkaaw ŋǣwi yedda syanri ăbărtamh nyalranakǣ̄.
Ŋămgǣ păsi nyu ŋanih yenărmana piŋgu,
Măniyeǣwa nyenǣcyaq ŋǣwaq tikăana ŋuliq ŋokaq, tǣri tikaana ŋoniq.
puna yednih tyer ma pirdirtanih mănʹ widărăbqnani maqniwq yoŋgmi săp-ir tyuku tibkaqyaqănăni,
Tuh ǣwăna yekar ŋămgǣrkaawmh mănǣqŋaq tuda pinyaŋi ǣwuwna.
Maqniwq: «Syaarih ti anyeda ăbărti adabăt tikăana yedamd ărt tyedibăir,
Ŋandowh, yedămda tyedada yah ni soqǒyda nyaŋǣdya siqiw ăbărtămh piryeqmaq niqimŋaq tiki yed ŋămgǣh ăncyerq ŋǣdakǣ̄ anih,
«Tyedah yaani lăŋgana ŋamdyodadmh ŋaat ŋamdyolawamih ilyewah yambanh».
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi yath ti ŋămgǣh pirkăna irsuh ŋăworŋaah Syudbya wǣsakomh măniyedā tarsih tyuki widărăŋō.
Muŋgoh pyay ăbir syudbyaq moncăŋgăqyaq tăsih yaah ith tyalkaădtasyetida.
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi mannaqmaq: «Mănʹ myakni ayadmh,
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi nyanda tad Syudbya wǣsăkoh pumna Muŋgoh pyay ăbi nidawh nǣkălh,
Syaarih unat yadbăti ŋodh ŋulih yalǣma,
syudbyako asryeqǣh yernya ŋobh syudbyako yesya sălqyaq nyenǣcyah lih yamb,
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi tăryemh sirŋa yesya salh ǣwana ŋulih yalăndoh almyerq liq.
almyerq liq ŋulih ŋaranda ŋulih tikaăna ŋaq.
«Tyuku yesya salh yedh ninih manondh niqnimh,
Sidya syudbyar ŋuwo niŋga syaarih piruwna ŋuwo niŋgnakǣǣh,
Tiki syudbyar nyaarq sawna ibq păŋgălnidawh abǣyq ŋumqyaq tikiq.
Syudbya wǣsăko nidawh uraq yesya mih yedh,
«Yuq tibyamh nibqnand pirasq ma tyuku maqniwq yesya săland yedh ti aŋgun, maqniwq,
ăcyah syurămba nyambor ŋămgǣq taykuh miŋgăda ŋuwocyaiq ŋămgǣda tănya,
syudbyako yesya salanh tyebwanda syerh yesyamh pyata tibkah tucyeyq wirkădaq.
ti tikaăna mǣbqni tăryemh siqmi mǣŋgosan?»
Maqniwq: «Sit toqǒla wǣnyekomh tibkaăna niw săpăŋguq,
Tăryemh sirŋa maqniwq mi toh tyaah tăryemh sirŋa anih,
yesya sălămda syudǣǣyuta poŋgăna nyǎlonda miŋa tănya ŋădʹbăta,
yootah tad ŋǣdăwanda yaănanda tănya ŋădʹbăta syudǣǣyuta pomna pilibth pakăl-yh tiki yootada.
Ŋani siqiw yalyah ŋanih oni anih, maqniwq:
syudbyaqyaqda soo myata nyoh sin tǣwotăŋo tădăw nyambor.
Ti maqniwq: «Ilyewah yambănh tǣwodăwǣmi ow maqniwq nyero yaah tyer ŋăwoqmami maqniwq ŋarănda ŋawoqmaădani tyedah maqniwq ti,
maqniwq ŋaătănda maqniwq taŋok tăŋociye tyer maqniwq ŋămgǣq wiqcipoyh wunisaq aŋguq,
todabcyaqyandoh ǣwanh tikanh puucyada pǣrŋada anih,
tiki muŋgar tikăana ŋǣqniwq yesyaăna urawiwa,
Mănʹ yǎnămbowna myattyudāmh anih myatoh anyerq myuq.
tăryemh sirŋadǣ̄mhsindya nyaŋi ǣwana maqniwq nye nyuda ŋǣwnawh maqniwq tikaăna maqniwq nyenǣciye [nyeracbortʃiwo] tikaăna mǣwi.
«ǣy, adǣymh tadawa maqniwq sinyakurkaq anʹq maqniwq tyaananda [nyeracbortʃiwo]».
Maqniwq tikaawaana tikimh nyunda watormamh namdăăwa maqniwq taralkaya maqniw tyuulmăndamih niwŋaq sidya sidyaat taral-yaq tad nǣkălmandih ŋob taqlyooy to.
«iy yōo maqniwq tadawa maqniwq ancyerq tăryerkamh tadyebya ŋǣya».
Tyedaawh maqniwq taki ti maqniwq nyenǣy maqniwq tyuku [nyeracbortʃiwo].
Syudbyani myakna mălye syanh tyukǒona ilyebaqni ŋodh maqniwq syudbyah nye nyuh waqăwana.
Pyelyeynyana maqniwq ŋopoy asăwa nyuda piya yarakoqyaq.
Piyada maqniwq nyaŋǣdya maqniwq yumbărad syedah ŋar,
Tuh ŋǣǣyuda tuh sidya ǣwuwna mǣŋguuyuda maqniwq myata tyaănyaŋi ǣw maqniwq ŋopoyriŋǣ nyāănda masʹ,
Ŋămgǣh piruwna ŋǣbqnanda ŋodh wǣsăkoqyaq săwuma,
tyeda taykuy syeŋgănya asăwamh tyedah mănʹ adaŋguw.
Manʹ tyedah mi myaqni măkodah sinh,
yesya wadămi ti tanyanyoq tyuriq tyuliba mǣta yesyǎ wădămi.
tyuqud nǣkăltawā anih, mănʹ tikaawaăd tiwa adăŋguwwa.
Wǣsăkoqyada ŋodh pinh ăya syudbya wǣsăkoqyand puucya ŋarŋociyeda nǣkălŋa.
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi muncih tăryemh incyelyewa.
tyedanda tyeda ti piribtyawa wadaqnanda nyeda ŋǣdaki.
Măkodah siina tikăăna ŋǣda tiki yesya wădamh tyaănyaŋi piya yarăkoh mǣnh tyebdyeda,
Syudbya wǣsăko tyormh nyadqmyacʹ nidawh nǣkălh.
«Ti wǣnyekow maqniwq tăryemh sit mǣŋgosadmh măqniwq,
ta ŋaruwnanda mǣǣna siqmi yootaana siqmi yǎdpinwa maqniwq,
Piya yarăkond maqniwq mǣda sooh sidya yaduwna maqniwq sidya yutyekăda măntircʹ ǣbyanondih.
ŋanih ŋobăŋguna Muŋgo pyay ăbi tăryemh incyelye,
Manih tyedah nye nyumih nyedănda anăwanh ărwa siqmi tăryemh mayedambiwa.
tiki păsih nyu puucyaqyada ŋanih onărawih.
tiki wǣsakor tyorkosăwǣyh nidawh nǣkălah puucyamda.
Sooh sidya yawna tăryemh wǣsoda mănrircʹ ǣwănondōh,
pih ŋanih tyeda ăncyerh myadh myumnya yadǣlina?»
Syudbya wǣsakoh nye nyu maqniwq: «Tyedah wunin andāh maqniwq tyedah irimd adăŋguqniqnawh,
taryemh ti ilyenaawaand tyedah laăna yah nyenǣcyaŋǣ wunin andh».
maqniwq ŋămgǣ mutraăna adā săwă ŋǣdăki,
maqniwq tyuku yaāmd maqniwq ŋulih malămbida.
ŋilʹnyarih ma siqiw yǎŋorǣyq mih mǣnh aqawrad.
Yonǣdǣǣnanda yaah nyah lǣbtăna syudbyako tidǣh ŋǣŋgu,
miq ŋamdyodaq tyuku tikiqyaq tiki ŋămgǣ pălka,
Ti lukq ŋamdyodāq aniq mǣ̄ nyānd sirtaq maqniwq mi mi ti orkiq totryewh tiki nyānd tǣri sirtaqmaq,
Maqniwq ilye yada tănya maqniwq ŋuliq ŋuliq piyariănda yǎdad piyānda,
tidǣh malăna  yaah nyayuh lǣbta tikaăna syudbyako mi ŋamdi,
mi pǣdăra yah orkiqyaq nyumda ŋămgǣ?
A, luk luk lukoh, ti lukqyaq.
maqniwq mi yaah nyah sirta maqniwq.
Ti tikawna maqniwq mǣnd yambănh ŋilʹnyah yanh mǣnh yeqŋaq lăngrinh sirta maqniwq».
«Mǣqmanda yalyand tănyabh maqniwq miŋgăr(muŋgăr) piyānda tyebăŋgu».
«Ŋămcaăndā tyebbăt aŋgăna niŋaq tikar ŋanih nisyerŋa».
Muŋgoh pyay ăbi tănyaŋi ǣwănda tănăwanda syerh nyenǣsyanda ŋodh tikăana luk ŋamdi.
Tiki lukămd taslaăya tad pitărmanda yaanda tyuku mǣqyada ti orkih piyǎraa niwŋaq aniq,
tănya ŋădʹbăta ăryoy myuykocyǎda tamӣnda malyē anih lukqyaq mǣnda paandh tidǣnda paăndh tah măntǣyq.
Tiki ŋinănda muŋgsăwǣyh irinda ărta ŋinda ŋǣqnisawq tăryemh anaqnidawh,
syudbya wǣsăkoh nye nyunh maqniwq: «Mănʹ myakni andadmh».
Siqiw yurq uryodah tǣda siqiw yonarq.
nuwoh saryoăna maqniwh siqiw yurh uryodah maqniwq ǣŋgrimh mǣqŋawaq,
sirah ŋǣdakih  siqiw yurq uryodamh syaartămboyh nidoh yuribyuq –
Tuh yash putkor syaqniqrinda ŋo(d)h ŋǣbqnanda ŋo(d)h –
Tădawa numh narah nyaŋǣŋǣ pilibtariq ayō,
«Tyuquy tiq ninya ma yamb idya tănya,
ma nyerh orkih yaykocyamh syurŋadamcʹ tikanh».
Ti tikănda asăwada tăryemh syurpi mǣkocyadămda,
mari yesida ǣnyakiq tikăad yaaq ăyaq.
Syaqnǣqrinda unănda ŋǣbqnanda ŋodh yaămh madăwiq.
mălye yaah salth mălye măriŋǣ ǣwi anih,
Tiki abtyeăbida tiki yaah yerʹh tad widărawadih yaănandih,
sadih niklǣ̄ anih tiki yaah yernya ănsawǣyh nyeŋǣ tiki ănanda ninya ŋamdyo tikăana aiwa tǣǣyuda ăyaa.
Tădaw tiki ănanda ninya padraah ănanda ninya tadh taăbyad yendh anada,
Yendh anada anih to asăwada sidya sǣrmh mǣta yat ănyad ŋămgǣ̌ǣd tobqnanda ŋodh,
tădaw maqniwq padraah anmh yarka nidawq irkādtaq,
Mănʹ ănmi anā anih nyudyercʹ anada maqniwq măncyaw yada ăyadmh,
Tiki yaăna maqniwq onawaana wada yǎŋgoya,
padraah ăn maqniwq marcʹ lǣni tyaah maqniwq siibtasʹ ŋǣwah inyaananda solada tǣsuyh.
Ŋǣwah inyaananda maqniwq padraah ănmh marcʹ lǣni tyaah maqniwq ǣdh ǣkaādtawǣ̄,
maqniwq wari myakna maqniwq Wǣǣlya wǣsăko iriwaq tănyǎsyǎti.
Sirah yambana myuyko myuykota siqimnya maqniwq tuda ŋădʹsyati
sidya tyusipoyh nyani tǣri sirŋa tăryemh ŋadʹbăta».
Wadăwa sinyana miqnimh mǣsyǎtinyoq tănyana măndalaŋguq inqniqimhtǣtamboyaqna.
tiki ălcoqlǣmh tăd modā anih tyeǣ asăwanda ănh tiki mǣnh,
ănh mǣnh ancăth tucʹ ŋurkăda(wirkăda) nyenǣciyeq pomna,
Tikād ŋanih tyuquq mǣda mǣmda myuykonda pyelyah pita,
«ănmi yarkqmadand maqniwq niwǣr ŋǣbqnand yarkq yendh siqmi anăŋgusʹ».
Ti tikăawaad tyey nyedah myumnya taminda yaamh mădănakǣda ănyada mădah ŋămgǣh.
Sirănda aqămqmaad yǎtrih tăryemh nyaarq Tǣsʹdanda syenyey syanormiq myatoh ŋoqmaqaqtǣwih tyuku ăncyerq ŋaq ŋămgǣh?
Wih tyer ilyenya nyenǣcyaŋǣ nirawinyoq anʹh.
Syenyah ti sita anaqcyaqnyoq tiki myadǣǣdandoh niwidq yamdaq,
Tǣri yarumā anih ŋarka Tǣsʹda nikanda waqawah pomna ulcotoliq.
Nikanda nyenǣy ubtădmh niryeta ŋarka ăr tăniwāsʹ,
tănyǎ tyaăkuy tyuku miq ŋarq noyq labăsq mǣŋǣ mǣtaq ŋamdyorŋǣ yathmǣtaq,
ŋămgǣŋǣ mǣtaq yath miq tănyacʹ tikăana.
Yekar maq(niqd)amh tinik yekar ŋămgǣ ŋǣdaki, ti.
Sirah yambana tăryemh niwh yadah syowna antaq minq wuniq tănyaq,
Syanrinda unh yadbata ŋodh piliq widărăŋo tădawa.
Tăryemh taslambida syenyey sanda niklăqmaq yaa yaanh tǣwih,
Yeǣy, laănăkor tyeǣ miq nyana ăyow,
«Nyoyq mărălyaŋgh maqniwq nye nyu maqniwq tyaănd syadota nye maqniwq syernaq tǣta nyawaq,
maqniwq tikih nye nyu maqniwq tiki mǣsʹ tara maqniwq».
ărămh nisʹ mǣsǣ̄q Nyoyq măqrădyaŋgh nye nyumh tiki nyemh mǣq.
Tiki nyemh mǣqmaqadăndoh syanrindoh unh ilyenakiq anih?

Tiki nye tiki Nyoyq măqrădyaŋg nyuuyuta asăwaŋǣ tiki nyenyada tiki tiki 
yunabh,
nyenyamda ti tyukuh tyukuh nyeŋǣ asăwaănda ti miqŋaduma anih.
Tiki asăwar syaqnirinda unănda ădryoq ănyamna tănyamna ŋǣdălyortaki.
Tyuku, tiki nyend yusyedasʹh mih nih paŋglyokoh nih nultawǣda,
tiki nyemh pǣŋada anih, tyeǣ madrota yaah ǣwanhanada.
Myaq tiki asawand Noy mărădyaŋgh yuna mǣtăda noyda tănyawi ŋobtiki tiki noyhtoqǒla.
Nyabi ŋamdyorta nihmǣda tiki myadh myuh tah ayeda,
ǣ̄y, ŋămgǣh pirkana maqniwq sǣwni ŋădimyaq.
Sǣwni ŋădimyaq maqniwq syadnyah ŋamdiwah ăncyerq ŋa,
Ti niwŋaq, syowna anta ŋăwăr tănyaŋawq?
Tănyah tǣwqmaawaădănda Noy mărădyaŋgawar myadh ancowna inrada myata anyerh ancowna.
Tikayeǣwaăd Noy mărădyaŋgawar tikari yaana tӣ tiki tăndh tiki lǣtămbidăwa,
tiki noy yoormh tad yoqmăda yaananda,
«Tiki noy ănyana aya, tiki noy ănyana ăya!»
ărămh nisʹ mǣsq tiki asăwaad ŋacyekimh o tiki nyer,
Ti tikand nye abtărka ŋǣqniwq Noy mărădyaŋgănd nye,
pǣdăraana tăryemh ilyewaănda tiki ŋacyekǣcyar niqimh yadǣlq.
nyabi pida ŋaāt asăwada ŋǣwanonda nyabi nyabi tyedah tyuku nyunda nisya ŋǣwanonda Noy mărădyaŋg.
Ңǣdalyowanondih nyaantih laanawanondih mamonondih tyedah nyabi mamononda ma tyedah mǣǣnih tyuku yaah nyencawǣǣna nyertyeңgoonih.
Mi uyumih nyamda nyertyeda maqniwq tikiyumih nyemda anaңguda Noy mărădyaŋg mamononda nyertyeǣrtabqnand mamononda ңǣqniwq mi niw tath maqniwq mi,
Tadawa tiki asawaah tad tikan nultadima myata anyerq ǣwanh.
Ңobh ңǣsiqңaq tiki nyenǣciyed pyeryenitoh nyah tikitoh yambanh.
Tiki yaad tadawa ti Noy mărădyaŋg anh wǣynyah ңacyekimh ңabtadawa,
pida ani tiki ңaat asawanda arta nyerdanda asawanda anh wǣynyah tiyq.
Tadawa myadoh nimnya tad ңadimyandoh taki myakq tad tǣwwadoh yaandoh ti ңǣqniwq.
Nyabir ңacyekimh pǣmbiwa nyabir nyemh pǣmbiwa yedǣy mi nyeboy nyemh mǣwi nyenǣcʹh.
Nyeңǣ tadawa yanh aqmiq aniq anya uyumgart myath wuni myattyuq aniq tyeǣ Wǣǣlya irinda myadh nyana ǣqniwq,
anda tad iprawanda  tiki anand myunya nyaңǣdya myaq ңǣwi.
Ti, tiki myat tad myarwanda yesʹ,
yesʹ ңuq mi yesʹ ңǣsoңotoh syerq ңud sandawa latar ңǣdaki nyaңǣdya myaq ңǣwi aniq,
Wari myaqңǣ myarada myata taaw ti ңaat sidya sǣrmh mǣta asawada tari myattyu.
Ti nyabi asawanh nyumda miqңaq pǣdaraana mayandorcʹ owǣmda nyabi asawar nyemda aye.
nyenǣciyeni ңokawna yaңgumcʹ pǣңga pǣyadq aniq tikanda tyuku laanakoh ңamgǣq nyaamna wadasyalmadmh.
Tyedah tǣri tyuku taryemh yeryemonda syerq syan laanakokocyaqyamh …
Ti tyuku laanakoi laanakokocyar ңodh tinyoq acyaq waalarkanyoq nyenǣy sabye laanako ninyoqңaq ңani tayna anda ңanih taki…
Miid ңodh mǣtʹtinaq(mǣcyatdinaq) niqimңaq tyedah anyaңǣǣna yabye aңolasʹtida tikid nyenǣy yath.
Tikadanda tandayarka wǣh ǣqmyaqarkaawaad ңanih syor ңod ңanih wuni arwaq yath.
Maqniw Salyeyakoyaqyeyңǣy Salyeyah sǣqryeqyeyңǣy ңawka sǣqryeqyeymңǣy,
nyaarq adǣtowңǣyh yaah madanowңǣy ңanoyeyңǣsyeyңǣy artoh tyaladowңǣyh ңawkah sǣqryeko.
Ti, syanmboy wadakoda tiki syomh mǣqmih.
Luciq, luciq anh siңǣy tyetǣy oramdaңǣy Salyeyakoyaqyeyңǣy ңilanda pyawidowңǣy taңi sǣlanaңǣy nyarmye lucidaңǣy lucandow anh siq.
Pida tida taki wacʹ mǣqңaqmaq yesi matorpa.
Yenyad ңarwǣ siqiwda pyebyada saltǣ toondoh yoracʹ ǣbtoh nilak adabtoh  taqwawdawǣyh niimcyatidohmyakandoh tobtoh nyabadoh nyeqyaq todoh ңuq paandq moyocyatida.
Nikadoh mancʹti ңamgǣ moyopid yaananat tiwak wakcyamh niwiq tatǣyq.
Lǣqmoqrakor tadawa nyabakonda nyah sidyamboңǣ ilyeңaah.
Nyabi abyeyq taңocyaңgana aniq sidya abi ilyeңaah.
Ңawi syaqniq ңǣbta ңodh Lǣqmoqrakor abiiyuta myath aya
abiiyuta myath aya aniq abiiyuta tiq ninya yewǣydih ңa ayowi.
sidya abir towonodih aniq Lǣqmoqrakor makodah siwnya nyalkara.
Sidya abiiyud tad manǣqңadih yewǣynih syancyoko ibya ңam-yada?
Taryemh syanri unandh yadwi uh Lǣqmoqrakor  usuwǣy yalyah turcyati,
mi anye ǣqmyaqad abiiyuta yewǣyh syancyoko ңamcyatida.
Ңamgǣ syaqniq ңǣbtoh ңodh yewǣyh syancyoko ңawortaanda yurwi niwңaq wunida namdq abiiyut towamh.
Lǣqmoqrakomh nyaqmaqdih maqniqimh tyedah yewǣynih syancyoko ңawortan tin ңǣsyatwinanyoq manih sit adaңgunih.
“Ңuliq yabtkoyenh siqmi nyodih ayeq maqniwq Ңǣbt yambamh   tabcakǣdmh nyabakomi tabcakǣdmh.q
Tadawa mi Lǣqmoqrakor myakanda niwq anʹq aniq nyabakoonda maqniwq mi:
Maqniwq sidya abiih siqmi nyaqamңaancʹ aniq maqniwq siqmi siqmi adawanh arwaңaancʹ sidya abiih nyah sit watorңadmh.q
“Ңuliq yabtkoyenh mi siqmi nyon adaq sidya abinh sit nidmh mitq.q
Piyakoowami udq tawnaw piyakoowami siwi sǣrkana yesya yaңgabcyami
Murtikaawami udq tawnaw tah myaqni ңuq.
Tokcyaabi udq tawnyan sirah myaqni ңuq.
Pro alyeya i pro woronu u myenya bilo.
Yaydamyeǣyq pukdamyeǣyq ңariq todoowq myeryeqңayoow nyerdandoow lyeǣbtǣyeǣyq sibyalyaңgǣǣy marǣyh oboow.
Cnatʃit, ulyetaytye bistryeye, a to puli lyetyat wam nawstryetʃu.
Aa, ʒalyet tʃtobi i nye ubiwali.
Nyunyoow nyunyoow ayel taңǣǣyq saryor anoowq nyunyoow nyunyoow.
